#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A 2D game object, inherited by all 2D-related nodes. Has a position, "
"rotation, scale, and Z index."
msgstr "一个2D游戏对象，是所有2D相关节点的父级。具有位置、旋转、缩放和Z索引。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node2d.rst:19
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_node2d.rst:21
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A 2D game object, with a transform (position, rotation, and scale). All "
"2D nodes, including physics objects and sprites, inherit from Node2D. Use"
" Node2D as a parent node to move, scale and rotate children in a 2D "
"project. Also gives control of the node's render order."
msgstr "一个具有位置、旋转和缩放的2D游戏对象。所有2D物理节点和精灵都继承自Node2D。使用Node2D作为一个父节点，在一个2D项目中移动、缩放和旋转子级。还可以控制节点的渲染顺序。"

